What is Monolith?

A Monolithic Architecture is when the entire application runs as a single unit (single service, single deployable, single DB).

Right now your banking project = Monolith ✅
(Account + Transaction + User everything inside one Spring Boot app)

Structure of Monolith
banking-system
 ├── controller
 ├── service
 ├── repository
 ├── entity
 ├── config
 └── util


Everything runs together in one JVM + one database

